  <brief_title>Comparison of Nexfin Pulse Contour Analysis and Cardiac Magnetic Resonance Imaging for the Measurement of Cardiac Output</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is Arterial Pulse Contour Analysis Using Nexfin a New Option in the Non-invasive Measurement of Cardiac Output? - A Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
